   -   [type SentinelOption](#SentinelOption \"type SentinelOption\")\n        -   [type SimpleCache](#SimpleCache \"type SimpleCache\")\n        -   [type StandaloneOption](#StandaloneOption \"type StandaloneOption\")\n        -   [type ValkeyError](#ValkeyError \"type ValkeyError\")\n            -   [IsValkeyErr(err)](#IsValkeyErr \"IsValkeyErr(err)\")\n            -   [(r) Error()](#ValkeyError.Error \"(r) Error()\")\n            -   [(r) IsAsk()](#ValkeyError.IsAsk \"(r) IsAsk()\")\n            -   [(r) IsBusyGroup()](#ValkeyError.IsBusyGroup \"(r) IsBusyGroup()\")\n            -   [(r) IsClusterDown()](#ValkeyError.IsClusterDown \"(r) IsClusterDown()\")\n            -   [(r) IsLoading()](#ValkeyError.IsLoading \"(r) IsLoading()\")\n            -   [(r) IsMoved()](#ValkeyError.IsMoved \"(r) IsMoved()\")\n            -   [(r) IsNil()](#ValkeyError.IsNil \"(r) IsNil()\")\n            -   [(r) IsNoScript()](#ValkeyError.IsNoScript \"(r) IsNoScript()\")\n            -   [(r) IsRedirect()](#ValkeyError.IsRedirect \"(r) IsRedirect()\")\n            -   [(r) IsTryAgain()](#ValkeyError.IsTryAgain \"(r) IsTryAgain()\")\n        -   [type ValkeyMessage](#ValkeyMessage \"type ValkeyMessage\")\n            -   [(m) AsBool()](#ValkeyMessage.AsBool \"(m) AsBool()\")\n            -   [(m) AsBoolSlice()](#ValkeyMessage.AsBoolSlice \"(m) AsBoolSlice()\")\n            -   [(m) AsBytes()](#ValkeyMessage.AsBytes \"(m) AsBytes()\")\n            -   [(m) AsFloat64()](#ValkeyMessage.AsFloat64 \"(m) AsFloat64()\")\n            -   [(m) AsFloatSlice()](#ValkeyMessage.AsFloatSlice \"(m) AsFloatSlice()\")\n            -   [(m) AsFtAggregate()](#ValkeyMessage.AsFtAggregate \"(m) AsFtAggregate()\")\n            -   [(m) AsFtAggregateCursor()](#ValkeyMessage.AsFtAggregateCursor \"(m) AsFtAggregateCursor()\")\n            -   [(m) AsFtSearch()](#ValkeyMessage.AsFtSearch \"(m) AsFtSearch()\")\n            -   [(m) AsGeosearch()](#ValkeyMessage.AsGeosearch \"(m) AsGeosearch()\")\n            - 